24:55.360 --> 24:56.727
- Oh my God.
- Buddy, I'm so sorry.

24:56.728 --> 24:58.162
- Is he okay?

24:58.163 --> 25:00.283
I'm so sorry, he ran right
out before I could see him.

25:00.307 --> 25:01.432
- It's not your fault.

25:01.433 --> 25:02.766
- You're the
sweetest dog, Buddy.

25:02.767 --> 25:04.635
- Tiger, Tiger, are
you guys okay?

25:04.636 --> 25:05.570
- Yeah.

25:05.570 --> 25:06.505
- Buddy, are you okay.

25:06.506 --> 25:09.507
- Allison, this is Mr. Frank.

25:09.508 --> 25:11.642
- Hi.
