here of all places?

25:32.197 --> 25:34.798
- Actually, um, I'm a writer.

25:34.799 --> 25:36.367
- You don't look like a writer.

25:36.368 --> 25:38.869
- No?
- No.

25:38.870 --> 25:40.070
