playin' football.

25:52.284 --> 25:54.218
- Okay, well, you tell
him I'm lookin' for him?

25:54.219 --> 25:55.686
- Mm hmm.
- Yeah?

25:55.687 --> 25:56.687
- Okay.
- Okay.

25:56.688 --> 25:57.922
Tiger, I'm so sorry.

25:57.923 --> 25:59.723
Mr. Frank, it was nice
to meet ya, I gotta go.

25:59.747 --> 26:02.126
My dad's gonna kill me,
but I'm so sorry, Tiger.

26:02.127 --> 26:03.527
- Bye, Allison.

26:03.528 --> 26:04.728
- Drive safely.

26:04.729 --> 26:05.896
- Thank you.

26:05.897 --> 26:07.598
- Allison likes me.

26:07.599 --> 26:09.601
I, I got me a girlfriend.

26:27.252 --> 26:29.520
- When are you
gonna finish this?

26:29.521 --> 26:31.256
- Workin' on it.

26:33.491 --> 26:34.559
- Well.

26:35.727 --> 26:37.461
It's gotta be done.

26:37.462 --> 26:39.530
Just stop your bitchin'.

26:39.531 --> 26:41.131
- I'm not bitchin'.

26:41.132 --> 26:42.434
- Okay.

26:43.435 --> 26:46.570
What's this I hear about
you goin' out for, uh,

26:46.571 --> 26:48.172
homecomin' queen?

26:48.173 --> 26:50.508
- You ain't gotta worry
about it, I'm not doin' it.

26:55.380 --> 26:56.914
- Why not?

26:56.915 --> 26:59.235
You're the best-lookin' thing
in this town since your mama.

27:00.452 --> 27:03.120
- Well thank you, but we'd
have to find a formal dress

27:03.121 --> 27:05.956
and we just don't have that
kind of money right now.

27:05.957 --> 27:08.326
- Ah, so it's all my fault?

27:10.562 --> 27:12.122
- Well if you didn't
drink and piss away

27:12.146 --> 27:14.198
everything you make.

27:14.199 --> 27:15.533
- What'd you say?

27:17.068 --> 27:18.670
Hey, what'd you say?

27:21.272 --> 27:24.209
You better watch that wise-ass
mouth of yours, little girl.

27:25.844 --> 27:28.146
You gonna get yourself
in big trouble.

27:32.784 --> 27:34.019
You hear me?

27:35.120 --> 27:36.721
Huh? - Yeah.

27:37.722 --> 27:38.757
- Yeah?

27:42.394 --> 27:43.595
All right.

27:46.097 --> 27:48.166
You can get all this
shit outta here.

28:08.987 --> 28:10.755
- Tiger! Tiger!

28:11.790 --> 28:14.058
Tiger, hey.

28:14.059 --> 28:15.225
What are you doin'?

28:15.226 --> 28:17.394
- Your lawn needs, needs
cuttin' real bad.

28:17.395 --> 28:18.562
Can't you see?

28:18.563 --> 28:20.464
- I can see that,
Tiger, but I don't.

28:20.465 --> 28:22.399
- First time's free.

28:22.400 --> 28:24.468
And, and, and since
this one's so small,

28:24.469 --> 28:26.670
I'll do it twice for nothin'.

28:26.671 --> 28:30.341
After that it's, um,
three times for $20.

28:31.276 --> 28:33.377
Or four times for 15.

28:33.378 --> 28:35.512
- Are you sure?

28:35.513 --> 28:37.681
- I'm sorry but
that's just business.

28:37.682 --> 28:40.285
- Wow, is that how you
get all your customers?

28:41.786 --> 28:43.754
Well you are very smart.

28:43.755 --> 28:47.157
- No, no, not me,
but Buddy, he's,

28:47.158 --> 28:48.659
he's the smartest dog ever.

28:48.660 --> 28:49.693
- Is he?

28:49.694 --> 28:50.961
- Mm hmm.
- Yeah?

28:50.962 --> 28:52.196
You sure love him.

28:52.197 --> 28:53.797
- Of course I do, Buddy.

28:53.798 --> 28:55.099
He's my best buddy.

28:55.100 --> 28:57.334
- Hi, Buddy.

28:57.335 --> 29:01.004
All right, Tiger, well thank
you for cuttin' our grass.

29:01.005 --> 29:01.940
- Okay.
- Lord knows

29:01.941 --> 29:03.040
nobody else'll do it.

29:03.041 --> 29:04.743
Thank you.

29:12.817 --> 29:13.818
- Buddy.

29:15.754 --> 29:17.822
Buddy, I, I got me a girlfriend.

29:22.727 --> 29:24.261
- Hey, you've reached Elaine.

29:24.262 --> 29:26.563
Leave me a message and I
will call you right back.

29:26.564 --> 29:27.632
Thanks, bye.

30:05.136 --> 30:06.370
- Hi.

30:06.371 --> 30:07.504
Brenda?

30:07.505 --> 30:09.406
- Betty.

30:09.407 --> 30:11.609
What can I do for you, Mr.
Stephens?

30:13.645 --> 30:14.946
- They're very good.

30:19.117 --> 30:21.718
My God, my God, Betty.

30:21.719 --> 30:23.654
This pie, I, I can't
even describe it.

30:23.655 --> 30:24.989
It's like crack.

30:26.624 --> 30:29.059
You're a crack dealer, Betty.

30:29.060 --> 30:31.296
- Well I'm sure
that's a compliment.

30:34.165 --> 30:36.500
So I hear you're a writer.

30:36.501 --> 30:39.236
That sounds pretty excitin'.

30:39.237 --> 30:40.505
- Not really.

30:41.639 --> 30:43.174
It's a lot of alone time.

30:44.742 --> 30:46.711
- I like to read romance novels.

30:47.946 --> 30:50.849
I know it's silly,
but I just love 'em.

30:53.618 --> 30:57.487
- I can imagine livin'
in a place like this,

30:57.488 --> 31:00.257
you probably wanna
escape somehow.

31:00.258 --> 31:02.193
You guys don't even
have a movie theater.

31:03.161 --> 31:05.796
- There's a lot of
fine folk livin' here.

31:05.797 --> 31:08.499
Good people, just
tryin' to get by.

31:09.467 --> 31:12.336
It would be nice to
travel more though.

31:12.337 --> 31:13.571
See the world.

31:15.640 --> 31:18.942
- Well maybe when Lanny
retires, you can.

31:18.943 --> 31:21.278
- Retire, shoot.

