after Roy was born.

32:18.803 --> 32:20.637
- Why?

32:20.638 --> 32:23.074
- Guess he thought she
was cheatin', somethin'.

32:24.342 --> 32:25.810
Who knows?

32:27.712 --> 32:30.781
I tell ya, I'm not one to
speak ill of the dead,

32:30.782 --> 32:33.817
but between you, me,
and the fence post,

32:33.818 --> 32:36.253
