in to raise 'em.

33:00.144 --> 33:02.946
She's a goddamn saint,
I tell you what.

33:02.947 --> 33:05.049
That lady is a goddamn saint.

33:06.484 --> 33:07.785
Hell yeah.

33:08.720 --> 33:10.788
