isn't it, Elaine?

33:48.451 --> 33:50.927
- I have no idea where
Peter is, Miss.

33:50.928 --> 33:52.496
- Smith.

33:52.497 --> 33:57.234
Oh come on, come on,
think real hard, Elaine.

33:57.235 --> 33:58.769
Come on, just use
your little head.

33:58.770 --> 34:00.203
Think real hard.

34:00.204 --> 34:02.139
- I don't know.

34:02.140 --> 34:04.341
- You're a very
attractive woman.

34:04.342 --> 34:05.809
- Please don't.

34:05.810 --> 34:07.850
- He hasn't reached out to
you even for a good fuck?

34:07.874 --> 34:10.510
- I haven't spoken to him
since he disappeared.

34:11.783 --> 34:14.018
- You're a terrible
liar, Elaine.

34:34.371 --> 34:35.772
- Gimme a T.

34:35.773 --> 34:37.074
- Somebody lookin'
at you, slick.

34:37.074 --> 34:38.241
- Gimme an I, I.

34:38.242 --> 34:40.143
