35:29.427 --> 35:30.495
- Dad.

35:37.935 --> 35:39.103
Thank you.

35:40.104 --> 35:41.472
- You're welcome.

35:45.376 --> 35:49.813
You know, uh, when
you're friend there,

35:49.814 --> 35:53.049
uh, that boy Roy Mitchell

35:53.050 --> 35:55.385
