and make a play, Roy.

36:17.594 --> 36:18.628
Can you do it, son?

36:18.629 --> 36:20.043
- Yeah, Coach, yeah, Coach!

36:20.044 --> 36:22.312
- Now get your tail out
there and make a play.

36:22.313 --> 36:24.153
- I'm gonna fuckin' run
right through you, boy.

36:24.177 --> 36:25.745
