37:00.451 --> 37:01.719
- Hey, Tiger.

37:02.687 --> 37:04.956
Your brother Roy's
pretty good, huh?

37:06.557 --> 37:08.593
- Yeah, I reckon
he's a good 'un.

37:13.331 --> 37:15.398
- Tiger, can I ask
you somethin'?

37:15.399 --> 37:17.667
- Uh huh.

37:17.668 --> 37:19.836
- How did you get
the name Tiger?

37:19.837 --> 37:22.739
- My, my mama said that
when, when I get somethin',

37:22.740 --> 37:26.076
